WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.400
The same 272 Old Faithful observations can be viewed cumulatively.

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:16.550
One npudist() call selects bandwidths optimized for the joint-distribution target
and estimates the probability at or below each eruption-duration
and waiting-time pair.

00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:20.500
This object is estimated directly, not by integrating the density.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:25.780
It opens in RStudio's Viewer, where you can rotate, zoom,
and resize the surface.

00:00:25.780 --> 00:00:28.800
Find the full script in Gallery Video Demos.
